#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/selecting/basics.rst:116
msgid "Circle Region Select"
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/selecting/basics.rst:119
msgid ""
"(*Circle Region Select*) is an example of selecting edges while in "
":guilabel:`Edge Select Mode`. As soon as an edge intersects the circle the "
"edge becomes selected. The tool is interactive such that edges are selected "
"while the circle region is being dragged with the :kbd:`lmb`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/selecting/basics.rst:121
msgid ""
"If you want to deselect elements, either hold :kbd:`mmb` or :kbd:`alt-lmb` "
"and begin clicking or dragging again."
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/selecting/basics.rst:124
msgid ""
"For :guilabel:`Faces` select mode, the circle must intersect the face "
"indicators usually represented by small pixel squares; one at the center of "
"each face."
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/selecting/basics.rst:128
msgid "To exit from this tool, click :kbd:`rmb`, or hit the :kbd:`Esc` key."
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/selecting/basics.rst:132
msgid "Lasso region"
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/selecting/basics.rst:134
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Lasso` select is similar to :guilabel:`Border` select in that you"
" select objects based on a region, except :guilabel:`Lasso` is a hand-drawn "
"region that generally forms a circular/round-shaped form; kind of like a "
"lasso."
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/selecting/basics.rst:136
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Lasso` is available in either :guilabel:`Edit Mode` or "
":guilabel:`Object Mode`. To activate the tool use the :kbd:`ctrl-lmb` while "
"dragging. The one difference between :guilabel:`Lasso` and "
":guilabel:`Border` select is that in :guilabel:`Object mode`, "
":guilabel:`Lasso` only selects objects where the lasso region intersects the"
" objects' center."
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/selecting/basics.rst:138
msgid "To deselect, use :kbd:`ctrl-shift-lmb` while dragging."
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/selecting/basics.rst:148
msgid "Lasso selection"
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/selecting/basics.rst:151
msgid ""
"(*Lasso selection*) is an example of using the :guilabel:`Lasso` select tool"
" in :guilabel:`Vertex Select Mode`."
msgstr ""

